{{flavour|Fires a shard of alchemical ice that coats whatever it hits with a layer of brittle frost which slows their movement.

Each shot fired will deplete the cannon's remaining durability, but if it survives to fire 5 times, the final shot will fragment to hit all enemies around the primary target for additional damage.}}

'''Hoarfrost Bullet''' is a monster-only spell which deals [[cold]] damage, automatically hits, and inflicts the [[Frozen]] status.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
{{CBA|0.32|this spell will be added to the game as part of [[Hoarfrost Cannonade]].}}
